CSN to Boost Minas Investment to 15 Billion Reais, Valor Says

-- B y   L a u r a   P r i c e
-- 
2011-03-09T10:53:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-09/csn-to-boost-minas-investment-to-15-billion-reais-valor-says.html
Cia. Siderurgica Nacional plans to
boost its investment in the Brazilian state of Minas Gerais to
15 billion reais ($9 billion) over the next few years, Valor
Economico said, citing the state government and the company.  CSN, as the steelmaker is known, in 2009 announced a plan to
invest 9 billion reais in the state, the Sao Paulo-based
newspaper reported.   To contact the reporter on this story:
